    away from Juliet\r\nAnd I was crying on the \nstaircase\r\nBegging you, Please
    don't go, and I said \r\nRomeo, take me somewhere we can be alone \r\nI'll be
    \nwaiting \nall there's left to do is run\r\nYou'll be the prince and I'll be
    the princess\r\nIt's a love story, baby, just say, \nYes"
